For Fixed-point

./configure --enable-debug --enable-intrinsics --enable-rtcd --enable-doc --enable-extra-programs X86_AVX_CFLAGS=-mavx --enable-fixed-point

so, SSE2/SSE4.1/AVX can be enabled for fixed only.


